{"lastModified":1772736735986,"uri":"c::7655158652::vessel::d5cc24ac-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744","yachtType":["Motor"],"description":"Operating Area: Balearics Islands, Mallorca, Menorca, Ibiza, Formentera, Cabrera\n\nLooking for an exceptional yacht charter experience in Mallorca? Look no further than our luxurious brand new Sirena 64 motor yacht. This meticulously crafted vessel boasts unparalleled space and comfort, making it the perfect choice for your next adventure on the water.\n\nDesigned with entertainment in mind, our Sirena 64 is ideal for socializing with friends and family. Multiple areas are available for relaxing and enjoying each other's company, while the spacious dining area is perfect for hosting special events.\n\nFor those seeking a bit of excitement, our yacht also features an impressive selection of water toys, providing endless opportunities for fun and adventure.\nReady to make your dream holiday a reality? Contact one of our knowledgeable yacht charter advisors today and book your unforgettable getaway on our Sirena 64 in Mallorca.\n\nAccommodates up to 12-day guests and six overnight guests in 3 well-appointed staterooms.  \n• 1 x Master Stateroom with King bed\n• 1 x VIP Stateroom with Queen bed\n• 1 x Guest Staterooms with Twin beds ","blueprint":{"name":"SALACIA","images":["/media/media::image::c::7655158652::vessel::d5cc24ac-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::b9f9ee70-f208-11f0-8ca9-b1e04aa5ad0a/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7655158652::vessel::d5cc24ac-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::b9f867d0-f208-11f0-8ca9-b1e04aa5ad0a/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7655158652::vessel::d5cc24ac-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::b9f97940-f208-11f0-8ca9-b1e04aa5ad0a/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7655158652::vessel::d5cc24ac-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::b9f9c760-f208-11f0-8ca9-b1e04aa5ad0a/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7655158652::vessel::d5cc24ac-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::b9fa1580